text: Kai Compagner (born 17 July 1969) is a Dutch rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Delft
